  "title": "Farm-level impacts of vertical coordination of the food supply chain: evidence from contract farming of milk in India",
  "abstract": "This paper quantifies the costs and benefits of contract farming of milk and identifies factors that influence farmers' participation in contract farming. Contract farming is more profitable than independent production.",
